title: Franco Battiato - Fleurs 2
description:
Franco Battiato - Fleurs 2
Audio CD (December 23, 2008)
Label: Mercury Italy
Rip 320kbs
All covers included.

Fleurs 2 is the 2008 album from Italian singer.
Part of his Fleurs trilogy, in which Battiato revisits some of his favorite standards.
The album features guest performances from Carmen Consoli (a duet on 'Tutto l'universo
Obbedisce All'Amore'), Sepideh Raisodat, Juri Camisasca, Antony & The Johnsons and Anne Ducros.
